data.description: This lovely, well maintained, large 3 bedroom, 2 bath home located in Summerview is marvelous and only 3 years only!!  Close to town with a country feel, the fenced in backyard and covered patio allow room for backyard entertaining or swimming in the above ground pool. The open floor plan is spacious and comfortable with luxury vinyl floors and 10 foot ceilings. The amazing kitchen showcases the granite countertops and lots of room. The Master bedroom has laundry room access through the master closet.
